    "headline": "StorageVault Announces Board Changes",
    "summary": "TORONTO, April 15, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- STORAGEVAULT CANADA INC. (“StorageVault” or the “Corporation”) (SVI-TSX) announces proposed changes to its Board of Directors to be submitted for approval at its upcoming annual general meeting of shareholders (the “Meeting”) to be held on Thursday, May 21, 2026 at 1:00 p.m. (Toronto time). At the Meeting, the shareholders of the Corporation will be asked to re-elect Iqbal Khan, Deborah Robinson, Steve Scott, Alan A. Simpson and Mary Vitug to the Board",
